  "title": "Junior Network Engineer/ IT Assistant (P)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Working Time :  Mon to Fri: 9am-6pm</strong></p><p><strong>Location:  Near Bendemeer MRT</strong></p><p><strong>Salary: $2,500 - $3,500</strong></p><p><strong>Job Duties:</strong></p><p>•        Assist with basic network setup (routers, switches, Wi-Fi)</p><p>•        Provide basic IT support (Windows & macOS)</p><p>•        Troubleshoot common IT issues (internet, email, printers, PCs/Macs)</p><p>•        Support Microsoft 365 / Google Workspace tasks</p><p>•        Perform on-site and remote IT support</p><p>•        Follow instructions from senior engineers and document work done</p><p></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>•        Strong interest in IT, willing to learn, and able to follow instructions</p><p>•        Basic computer skills (especially macOS/ Apple devices)with good attitude and communication</p><p>•        Basic networking knowledge or IT-related qualification is a plus</p><p><strong></strong></p><p><strong>Career Development:</strong></p><p>•        On-the-job training provided</p><p>•        Exposure to real SME IT environments</p><p>•        Opportunity to progress into Network / System Engineer role</p><p></p><p>*** Interested applicants are strongly encouraged to send in your resume or WhatsApp wa.me/6588543301  for more details ***</p><p></p><p>ELITEZ PTE LTD | EA 16C8004</p><p>TSAI PEI HUA PENNY | R1988862</p>",
